sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User / CA
    participant UI as CIQ UI
    participant IDP as SC IDP Gateway (SKE)
    participant AO as AI Orchestration Service
    participant GR as Guardrail Service (SKE)
    participant RT as Retrieval Service
    participant ES as Elasticsearch
    box AI Factory (Cloud)
      participant EMB as Embedding Endpoint
      participant LLM as LLM Endpoint
    end

    U->>UI: Submit query
    UI->>IDP: Authenticate + authorize
    IDP-->>UI: Token / claims
    UI->>AO: Query + user context
    AO->>AO: Routing + query expansion
    AO->>GR: Guardrail validation

    alt Guardrail pass
        GR-->>AO: Approved / sanitized query
        AO->>RT: Retrieval request
        RT->>ES: Native hybrid search
        ES->>EMB: Internal embedding call (ES-managed)
        EMB-->>ES: Embedding vector
        ES-->>RT: Hybrid results
        RT-->>AO: Retrieved context + metadata
        AO->>LLM: Prompt for response generation
        LLM-->>AO: Generated response
        AO-->>UI: Final response + citations
        UI-->>U: Render answer
    else Guardrail fail
        GR-->>AO: Block / policy violation
        AO-->>UI: Safe fallback message
        UI-->>U: Show policy-safe response
    end
